266
00:27:37,072 --> 00:27:38,113
Look at Lowenstein.

267
00:27:39,115 --> 00:27:41,283
Everything is just a little askew.

268
00:27:42,077 --> 00:27:45,496
Pretty soon, people think the old rules
are not in effect...

269
00:27:45,664 --> 00:27:48,999
...and break them, figuring nobody'll care
because it's emergency time.

270
00:27:49,501 --> 00:27:50,584
Time out.

271
00:27:50,752 --> 00:27:54,630
I can't figure out how you can be doing
advanced theoretical thinking like that...

272
00:27:54,798 --> 00:27:56,340
