273
00:27:56,633 --> 00:27:59,093
Lowenstein dreams of bigger things.

274
00:27:59,844 --> 00:28:01,762
Assistant county prosecutor
isn't the end.

275
00:28:01,930 --> 00:28:04,431
Someday, deputy county prosecutor.

276
00:28:04,599 --> 00:28:07,393
When the truth comes out
about dirt I've been involved in...

277
00:28:07,560 --> 00:28:10,104
...my future in this state
will be unlimited.

278
00:28:10,271 --> 00:28:11,980
GLENDA:
Hi, Ned.

279
00:28:13,858 --> 00:28:15,109
Hi, Glenda.

280
00:28:15,276 --> 00:28:17,194
[PETER LAUGHING]

281
00:28:35,630 --> 00:28:38,966
[MATTY BREATHING HEAVILY]

282
00:29:00,989 --> 00:29:02,030
NED:
You all right?

283
00:29:02,198 --> 00:29:04,867
Don't stop.

284
