You are killing me. I'm red, I'm sore.

285
00:29:09,414 --> 00:29:11,123
You're sore? You've got nerve.

286
00:29:11,332 --> 00:29:13,250
Look at it. It's about to fall off.

287
00:29:13,418 --> 00:29:16,503
Is there any more ice? I'm burning up.

288
00:29:29,893 --> 00:29:32,060
He's coming up tomorrow.

289
00:29:33,229 --> 00:29:35,689
I can't stand the thought of him.

290
00:29:36,316 --> 00:29:38,150
He's small...

291
00:29:38,318 --> 00:29:39,735
...and mean...

292
00:29:39,903 --> 00:29:41,570
...and weak.

293
00:30:55,728 --> 00:30:57,104
NED:
Hey, lady, you wanna fuck?

294
00:31:01,442 --> 00:31:02,609
Gee, I don't know.

295
00:31:04,195 --> 00:31:05,654
Maybe.

296
00:31:07,699 --> 00:31:11,118
- This sure is a friendly town.
- I'm sorry.

297
00:31:11,286 --> 00:31:12,744
You are?

298
00:31:12,912 --> 00:31:15,205
You mean, the offer is no good?

299
00:31:15,957 --> 00:31:17,291
I feel like a jerk.

300
00:31:17,959 --> 00:31:21,545
Well, maybe you were
supposed to deliver it next door.

301
00:31:21,713 --> 00:31:25,132
You must be looking for
the lady of the house.

302
00:31:25,300 --> 00:31:26,967
Ned, this is Mary Ann.

303
00:31:27,135 --> 00:31:31,305
MARY ANN: We were just meeting.
Ned made me feel very welcome.

304
00:31:31,931 --> 00:31:33,849
I am an idiot.

305
00:31:35,393 --> 00:31:36,977
How are you?

306
00:31:37,145 --> 00:31:38,228
Are you staying in town?

307
00:31:38,396 --> 00:31:40,981
MARY ANN:
No, no, just passing through.

308
00:31:41,149 --> 00:31:43,525
Nice area. A little hot for my tastes.

309
00:31:43,693 --> 00:31:47,154
It's unusual.
We're famous for our cool breezes.

310
00:31:47,322 --> 00:31:48,947
Wanna stay for dinner?

311
00:31:49,115 --> 00:31:50,908
MARY ANN:
I've gotta go.

312
00:31:51,075 --> 00:31:52,701
Got to go.

313
00:31:52,869 --> 00:31:54,494
Bye.

314
00:31:55,705 --> 00:31:57,664
You two have fun now.

315
00:32:04,172 --> 00:32:06,673
