316
00:32:09,427 --> 00:32:12,846
I'm sorry.
I gotta be more careful.

317
00:32:13,014 --> 00:32:15,349
Mary Ann is an old friend.

318
00:32:15,516 --> 00:32:17,726
She's like a sister to me.

319
00:32:17,894 --> 00:32:20,062
She wants me to be happy.

320
00:32:29,781 --> 00:32:31,365
NED:
How do you know?

321
00:32:31,574 --> 00:32:32,950
MATTY:
I saw the will once.

322
00:32:33,117 --> 00:32:35,035
